{"image_id": "AMZN_2008_page_45", "image_size": [1238, 1613], "ocr": [{"text": "Income Taxes", "bbox": [164.6, 140.2, 285.7, 161.0]}, {"text": "We recorded a provision for income taxes of $247 million, $184 million, and $187 million, in 2008, 2007,", "bbox": [185.5, 175.6, 1072.6, 196.5]}, {"text": "and 2006. The effective tax rate in 2008 and 2007 was lower than the 35% U.S. federal statutory rate primarily", "bbox": [143.8, 200.6, 1068.8, 221.5]}, {"text": "due to earnings of our subsidiaries outside of the U.S. in jurisdictions where our effective tax rate is lower than in", "bbox": [143.8, 225.6, 1091.4, 246.5]}, {"text": "the U.S. The effective tax rate in 2006 was higher than the 35% U.S. federal statutory rate resulting from", "bbox": [143.8, 250.6, 1019.2, 271.5]}, {"text": "establishment of our European headquarters in Luxembourg, which we expected to benefit our effective tax rate", "bbox": [143.8, 275.6, 1079.5, 296.5]}, {"text": "over time. Associated with the establishment of our European headquarters, we transferred certain of our", "bbox": [143.8, 300.7, 1019.4, 321.5]}, {"text": "operating assets in 2005 and 2006 from the U.S. to international locations. These transfers resulted in taxable", "bbox": [143.8, 325.7, 1054.8, 346.5]}, {"text": "income and exposure to additional taxable income assertions by taxing jurisdictions.", "bbox": [143.8, 350.7, 848.3, 371.5]}, {"text": "Our effective tax rate is subject to significant variation due to several factors, including from accurately", "bbox": [185.5, 396.1, 1050.9, 416.9]}, {"text": "predicting our taxable income, the taxable jurisdictions to which it relates, business acquisitions and investments,", "bbox": [143.8, 421.1, 1090.0, 441.9]}, {"text": "and foreign currencies. We have current tax benefits and net operating losses relating to excess stock-based", "bbox": [143.8, 446.1, 1040.2, 467.0]}, {"text": "compensation deductions that are being utilized to reduce our U.S. taxable income. As such, we expect a majority", "bbox": [143.8, 471.1, 1093.9, 492.0]}, {"text": "of our net tax provision to be non-cash.", "bbox": [143.8, 496.1, 471.9, 517.0]}, {"text": "Effect of Exchange Rates", "bbox": [164.6, 551.7, 384.2, 572.5]}, {"text": "The effect on our consolidated statements of operations from changes in exchange rates versus the", "bbox": [185.5, 587.1, 1006.6, 607.9]}, {"text": "U.S. Dollar is as follows (in millions, except per share data):", "bbox": [143.8, 612.1, 650.0, 632.9]}, {"text": "Year Ended", "bbox": [480.5, 652.2, 566.2, 668.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2008", "bbox": [456.0, 668.9, 590.8, 685.6]}, {"text": "Year Ended", "bbox": [710.5, 652.2, 796.2, 668.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2007", "bbox": [686.0, 668.9, 820.7, 685.6]}, {"text": "Year Ended", "bbox": [940.5, 652.2, 1026.2, 668.9]}, {"text": "December 31, 2006", "bbox": [916.0, 668.9, 1050.7, 685.6]}, {"text": "At Prior", "bbox": [416.5, 693.9, 476.3, 710.6]}, {"text": "Year", "bbox": [428.8, 710.6, 464.0, 727.2]}, {"text": "Rates (1)", "bbox": [414.8, 727.2, 478.2, 743.9]}, {"text": "Exchange", "bbox": [488.6, 693.9, 558.1, 710.6]}, {"text": "Rate", "bbox": [506.7, 710.6, 540.0, 727.2]}, {"text": "Effect (2)", "bbox": [490.3, 727.2, 556.4, 743.9]}, {"text": "As", "bbox": [591.1, 710.6, 609.6, 727.2]}, {"text": "Reported", "bbox": [567.0, 727.2, 633.7, 743.9]}, {"text": "At Prior", "bbox": [646.5, 693.9, 706.3, 710.6]}, {"text": "Year", "bbox": [658.8, 710.6, 694.0, 727.2]}, {"text": "Rates (1)", "bbox": [644.7, 727.2, 708.2, 743.9]}, {"text": "Exchange", "bbox": [718.6, 693.9, 788.1, 710.6]}, {"text": "Rate", "bbox": [736.7, 710.6, 770.0, 727.2]}, {"text": "Effect (2)", "bbox": [720.3, 727.2, 786.4, 743.9]}, {"text": "As", "bbox": [821.1, 710.6, 839.6, 727.2]}, {"text": "Reported", "bbox": [797.0, 727.2, 863.7, 743.9]}, {"text": "At Prior", "bbox": [876.5, 693.9, 936.2, 710.6]}, {"text": "Year", "bbox": [888.8, 710.6, 924.0, 727.2]}, {"text": "Rates (1)", "bbox": [874.7, 727.2, 938.1, 743.9]}